      "content": "<|channel>thought\n<channel|>That's a good start for the reference list. To make the satire really bite, I want to lean into the absurdity of these. For the \"tough, street-smart Latino guy\" or the \"nerdy Indian character\" ones, could you describe some of the specific, more extreme traits or behaviors that usually define them in these movies? Like, what exactly are the stereotypical ways they talk or act that people always make fun of?",
